        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.199999984
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.4000001112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな～、こんにちは～！　今日はサニーピースの\nバレンタインイベントに来てくれてありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone~ hello~! Thank you so much for coming to\nSunny Peace’s Valentine’s event today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4000001112,
      "endTime": 12.9378007093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1378005186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいるファンのみんなは……\n厳正な抽選をくぐり抜けたラッキーな人達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the fans here today are…\nlucky people who made it through a strict lottery…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1378005186,
      "endTime": 19.529955021299997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7232883928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "物凄い倍率だったらしいね\nみんな、チョコを買って応募してくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard the odds were insane.\nThank you all for buying chocolates and applying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7232883928,
      "endTime": 26.9023715494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.102371454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "落選した人が多かったから……お願いして、急遽\n配信もしてもらってる……配信のみんなも楽しんでね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since so many people didn’t get selected‚ we asked them to set up\na livestream at the last minute. Everyone watching online‚ enjoy it as well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.102371454,
      "endTime": 36.648244905300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.8415781813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "今回はライブの他に企画コーナーもやるんだけど\nサニピが今までやったことのないめずらしい企画なのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ besides the live show‚ we also have a special segment—\nit’s a rare kind of project Sunny Peace has never done before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8415781813,
      "endTime": 45.424889071500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.6115558145
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな私達が見られるのは\nひょっとしたら今日だけかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing us like this\nmight be something you can only experience today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6115558145,
      "endTime": 50.688880014199995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.8822131949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ここでしか見られない特別なサニーピースを\n楽しんでいってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please enjoy this special Sunny Peace\nthat you can only see here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8822131949,
      "endTime": 55.5224627333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.7357959904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、サニーピースのバレンタインイベント\n始めるよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then‚ the Sunny Peace Valentine’s event\nis starting~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7357959904,
      "endTime": 61.100000127099996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 407.3836009000047
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6787.995546799998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.2649798867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "以上、サニーピースメドレーでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was the Sunny Peace medley!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.29831322,
      "endTime": 66.3252292948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.5118958471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブで盛り上がったところで、次は企画コーナーよ\nみんな、準備はいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that we’re fired up from the live‚ it’s time for the special segment.\nEveryone‚ are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5118958471,
      "endTime": 73.3965444563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6032108941
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ついにこの時がきたわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So the moment has finally come…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6032108941,
      "endTime": 76.649129168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "覚悟完了……どんとこい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m ready… bring it on…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8624624488,
      "endTime": 79.6463854072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8530520358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ始めるわよ。バレンタイン特別企画！\nサニーピース胸キュン告白選手権～！　いぇーいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then let’s begin! Valentine’s Special Project!\nSunny Peace’s Heart-Fluttering Confession Championship~! Yay~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8530520358,
      "endTime": 90.6989247242,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2166.9263205999982
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.8922580002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "今から一人ずつ愛の告白をしてもらって\nファンのみんなを一番きゅんきゅんさせた人が優勝よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ each of us will make a confession of love‚\nand the one who makes the fans’ hearts flutter the most wins.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8922580002,
      "endTime": 98.9954324959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1820990482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに告白のセリフは、サニピのことが大好きな\nサニピの有識者かつ文章力のある人に考えてもらったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ the confession lines were written by someone\nwho loves Sunny Peace and has great writing skills.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1820990482,
      "endTime": 108.5834364812,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
          "delay": 2900.259653900008
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12784.567618499992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.7967695474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの恋愛マスター、伊吹渚プロよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The romance master of Hoshimi Pro—Pro Ibuki Nagisa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.7967695474,
      "endTime": 113.115499711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3221662919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、それじゃあ、今からみんなに台本を配るから\n自分の台詞を確認してね。初見の反応、期待してるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I’ll hand out the scripts now‚\nso check your lines. I’m looking forward to your first reactions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3221662919,
      "endTime": 123.8450914781,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13327.833708100003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.0517580112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "どんなセリフだろう……ドキドキしてきたよ……\n……ええっ！　このセリフをみんなの前で言うの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of lines are they…? I’m getting nervous…\n…Wha—! I have to say this in front of everyone!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0517580112,
      "endTime": 132.690481194,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9114.908655500003
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 18348.24198880001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8838144701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "私がこれを言うなんて、想像しただけで顔から\n火が出そうだわ。渚……恨むわよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just imagining myself saying this makes my face feel\nlike it’s on fire. Nagisa… I’ll hold a grudge…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8838144701,
      "endTime": 143.17830413989998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
