      "text": "みんながどんな告白をするのか楽しみだな～\nじゃあ、まずは私がトップバッターで行くね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m excited to see what kind of confessions everyone makes~\nOkay‚ I’ll go first as the opening batter!",
