      "text": "ではさくらちゃん！\n客席のみんなに向かって、愛の告白をどうぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ Sakura-chan!\nPlease give your confession of love to everyone in the audience!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.5228619972,
      "endTime": 172.8179868141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
