      "text": "あのね……キミといると、すっごく楽しくて\n世界がキラキラ輝いて見えるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know… when I’m with you‚ it’s so much fun\nthat the whole world looks like it’s sparkling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.1513183036,
      "endTime": 181.8557172218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
